<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Naqlun</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><g type="stauros"/> καταξιώσῃ ἡ ὑμετέρα
<expan>ποθειν<ex cert="high">ότης</ex></expan> <choice><corr>ἀποδιδόναι</corr><sic>αποδιδωναι</sic></choice> τὰς δύο <num value="2"/> ἀποχὰς ἃς
ἔχει, μίαν <num value="1"/>

    <lb n="2"/>λέγω τοῦ ἐπιμελητοῦ καὶ μίαν τοῦ γραμματέως, τῷ
κυρίῳ Τιμοθέῳ.
αὐτὸς γὰρ

    <lb n="3"/><choice><corr>ᾠκειώσατο</corr><sic>οικειοσατο</sic></choice> τὰ χωρία τῶν ἐποικίων. <add place="supralinear">καὶ</add> σημάνῃ μοι,
διὰ τοῦ
εὑρισκομένου παῤ αὐτῆς

    <lb n="4"/>ἐρχομένου ἐγγὺς ἡμῶν, καὶ τὴν ἀπόκρισιν τῆς κυρᾶς
Ἰωαννίας καθώς
εἶπον αὐτῇ

    <lb n="5"/>καὶ τῷ κυρίῳ Φιλοξένῳ. ἔρρωσθε ἐν
<expan>κ<ex cert="high">υρί</ex></expan>ῳ. <add place="supralinear"><g type="stauros"/></add> ἐγὼ δὲ απα Ὧρ
ἐθαύμασα εἰς τὴν μεγάλην σου φρόνησιν ὅτι

    <lb n="6"/>ἦλθες καὶ ἀπῆλθες καὶ οὐδέν μοι <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἀ</unclear><gap extent="1" reason="lost" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">έ</unclear>θου περὶ τῆς
γνώσεως τῶν
οἰναρίων. <subst><add place="inline">τί</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">το</del></subst> ἀπέβη περὶ τῶν ὀνομασθέντων παρὰ σοῦ

    <lb n="7"/>ἐσχηκέναι τὸν οἶνον; Πλὴν καλῶς ποιεῖτε δεχόμενοι
παραυτὰ τὰ ἴσα
. κοῦρι μούστου καὶ μὴ ζητῆσαι τιμὴν ἵνα κἂν

    <lb n="8"/>οὕτως δυνηθῶμεν πληρωθῆναι. <add place="supralinear"><g type="stauros"/></add>
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="9"/><subst><add place="inline">καὶ</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">ολ</del></subst> γὰρ τοῦτο ἤρεσεν τῷ πατρὶ ἡμῶν. γράψον μοι οὖν τὴν τοῦ πράγματος περιπέτειαν· καὶ πρὸς <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δὲ</unclear> Θεὸς ἀπολύει, λέγω σοι.

    <lb n="10"/>οἶδας γὰρ ὅτι οὐ θέλομεν παρενοχλῆσαι τὰς ἀκοὰς τοῦ πατρὸς ἡμῶν ὅτι ἐν πολλῇ ὀλιγωρίᾳ ἐστὶν διὰ τὴν ζημίαν ἣν 

    <lb n="11"/>ἠπαιτήθης. <g type="stauros"/>

    <lb n="12"/><g type="stauros"/> τῷ <expan>ποθειν<ex cert="high">οτάτῳ</ex></expan> μου υἱῷ <expan>κυρ<ex cert="high">ίῳ</ex></expan> Βασιλεῖῳ <expan>κόμ<ex cert="high">ετι</ex></expan> <g type="stauros"/> Νικόλαος <g type="stauros"/></ab></div></div><div n="meta.38394" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.38394" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="575" notBefore="526" type="textDate">Mitte VI</date></p></div><div n="meta.38394" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Naqlun</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">12</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">38394</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0248</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">12</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0248;;12" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.38394" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Plate XV</bibl><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">JJP 22, 1992, Fig. 2 (nach S. 12)</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.38394" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl default="NO" subtype="other" type="publication">SB XX 14513</bibl></div><div n="meta.38394" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="low" full="yes" type="ancientFindspot">Naqlun (Arsinoites)</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>